# =================================================================
# Explore-image-specific exclusions. Auto-picked by BuildKit when
# building with `-f Dockerfile.explore`. Common patterns (credentials,
# build artefacts, editor noise) live in the root `.dockerignore` and
# are NOT duplicated here — BuildKit reads only the matching sibling
# file when one exists, so we have to inline the common patterns too.
# =================================================================

# --- Common patterns (mirror of .dockerignore) ---
**/*-key.json
**/service-account*.json
**/service_account*.json
**/firebase-adminsdk-*.json
**/credentials.json
**/*-credentials.json
**/.env
**/.env.*

**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.cache/
**/*.bak
*.bak
**/coverage/
.coverage

.git/
.gitignore
.idea/
.vscode/
.DS_Store

# Private build narrative & scratch assets — NEVER bake into the public image.
# COPY does not honor .gitignore, so the root `.gitignore` `*PLAN.md` rule must
# be re-stated here. `**/PLAN.md` only matched a file literally named PLAN.md;
# the broader `**/*PLAN.md` also catches FACE_SEARCH_PLAN.md (real names) and any
# future *PLAN.md. The screenshots are face-search UI captures (real faces).
**/*PLAN.md
**/Screenshot*.png
**/Screenshot*.jpg
photo-search/*.png
photo-search/*.jpg

# Private data caches — NEVER bake into the public image. The real files live in
# ~/.cache (outside the build context); these guard against an in-repo copy, since
# COPY ignores .gitignore and the generic **/.cache/ rule wouldn't catch a stray copy.
**/hiking_image_ids.json
**/person_aliases.json
**/person_extras.json

# =================================================================
# Repo content unrelated to the explore image. The explore Dockerfile
# only COPYs four package dirs (photo-search, log-search, search-common,
# explore) plus albums*.json — everything else here belongs to the
# colorless-days static site, hiking-ui assets, k8s manifests, etc.
# Excluding them shrinks the build context dramatically.
# =================================================================
/CLAUDE.md
/HIKING-PLAN.md
/PLAN.md
/README.md
/Dockerfile
/.github/
/.dockerignore
/all.html
/app.js
/colorless-days/
/cv/
/folderIndex.html
/google*.html
/icon.png
/index.html
/k8s/
/nginx.conf
/preview.html
/styles.css
/photo_*.jpg
/photo_*.png
